==English==
===Alternative spellings===
* [[gra'mercy]], [[gra-mercy]]

===Etymology===
Middle English [[gramerci]], from Old French [[grant]] [[merci]] “great thanks.”

===Interjection===
'''gramercy'''
# [[thanks|Thanks]]; [[many thanks]]; an expression of gratitude.

===Noun===
'''gramercy'''
# [[thanks|Thanks]].
# (used as an exclamation expressing suprise or sudden strong feelings).

